OL,3,CParents awarded #20,000 in damages
OL,4,Cafter wrongful arrest over WhatsApp row
OL,6,FTwo parents who were arrested after
OL,7,Fcomplaining about their daughter's
OL,8,Fprimary school on WhatsApp have
OL,9,Freceived #20,000 in damages from the
OL,10,Fpolice.
OL,12,FMaxine Allan and Rosalind Levine told
OL,13,FITV News that for them, it was "not
OL,14,Fabout the money but about the
OL,15,Fliability", after their arrest was
OL,16,Ffound to be unlawful.
