OL,3,CParents awarded #20,000 in damages
OL,4,Cafter wrongful arrest over WhatsApp row
OL,6,FMs Levine said: "The impact this had
OL,7,Fon our children was really profound,
OL,8,Feven to this day and it should never
OL,9,Fhave happened. We're grown-ups, we can
OL,10,Fdeal with it but when it comes to
OL,11,Fdoing something like that in front of
OL,12,Fsmall, terrified children, there's
OL,13,Fjust no excuse."
