OL,3,CParents awarded #20,000 in damages
OL,4,Cafter wrongful arrest over WhatsApp row
OL,6,FIn a statement, Hertfordshire Police
OL,7,Fsaid: "Whilst there are no issues of
OL,8,Fmisconduct involving any officer in
OL,9,Frelation to this matter, Hertfordshire
OL,10,FConstabulary has accepted liability
OL,11,Fsolely on the basis that the legal
OL,12,Ftest around necessity of arrest was
OL,13,Fnot met in this instance.
OL,15,F"Therefore Mr Haddow-Allen and Ms
OL,16,FLevine were wrongfully arrested and
OL,17,Fdetained in January 2025. It would be
OL,18,Finappropriate to make further comment
OL,19,Fat this stage."
