OL,3,CParents awarded #20,000 in damages
OL,4,Cafter wrongful arrest over WhatsApp row
OL,6,FLast year, the couple had complained
OL,7,Fabout the recruitment process for the
OL,8,Fnew headteacher at Cowley Hill Primary
OL,9,FSchool, Borehamwood.
OL,11,FThese complaints were voiced on social
OL,12,Fmedia and in a private WhatsApp group.
OL,14,FCowley Hill Primary School reported
OL,15,Fthese comments to the police.
OL,17,FIn January this year, Mr Allen and Ms
OL,18,FLevine were arrested in front of their
OL,19,Fthree-year-old daughter. They were
OL,20,Faccused of harassment and malicious
OL,21,Fcommunication.
