OL,3,CParents awarded #20,000 in damages
OL,4,Cafter wrongful arrest over WhatsApp row
OL,6,FAfter the police officers turned up at
OL,7,Ftheir door, the couple were led away
OL,8,Fin handcuffs, in front of their
OL,9,Fneighbours and three-year-old daughter.
OL,11,FThey were held at the police station
OL,12,Ffor 11 hours before the case was
OL,13,Fclosed.
OL,15,FMs Levine told ITV News that the
OL,16,Ftrauma of the day meant she would
OL,17,F"never trust the police again".
OL,19,FNow, ten months later, the
OL,20,FHertfordshire Constabulary have shared
OL,21,Fthat they were unlawfully detained.
